<div n="1"><head>Epitaphiolum. </head><lb/>
<lg rendition="#aq" type="poem"><lg><l><hi rendition="#in">D</hi>Um vidit <hi rendition="#i">Pietas</hi> BECKHERI candida cippum</l><lb/>
<l>Prælargè plorans talia verba dedit:</l><lb/>
<l>„Noſter Amor ſitus hîc, hîc pôſta corona Galeni eſt:</l><lb/>
<l>„Hippocratis tanti neſcia Fama mori.</l><lb/>
<l>„Te benè poſſe mori ſtudeas hoc tempore peſtis</l><lb/>
<l>„Quisquis es: Hic labor eſt. <hi rendition="#i">Te bene poſſe mori</hi>.</l></lg></lg><lb/>
<p><hi rendition="#aq #c #et2">Ultimi honoris Magno, dum viveret,<lb/>
Amico habendi gratia<lb/>
faciebat</hi></p><lb/>
<p><hi rendition="#c #et2"><hi rendition="#aq">Rotgerus</hi> zum Bergen/<lb/>
